<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Section Number="0086.031" xmlns="http://StatRev.xsd"><Catchline xml:space="preserve">Before breach.</Catchline><SectionBody><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">A contract may be construed either before or after there has been a breach of it.</Text></SectionBody><History xml:space="preserve">s. 3, ch. 21820, 1943; s. 38, ch. 67-254.</History><Note><Text xml:space="preserve" Style="Intro">Former s. 87.03.</Text></Note></Section>